About Ogni Jugor Firingoti Moi

Listen to Ogni Jugor Firingoti Moi online. Ogni Jugor Firingoti Moi is an Assamese language song and is sung by Bhupen Hazarika, Samar Hazarika and Monima Saikia. Ogni Jugor Firingoti Moi, from the album Siraj (Original Motion Picture Soundtrack), was released in the year 1988. The duration of the song is 3:42. Download Assamese songs online from JioSaavn.
